        {
            "title": "英國和日本領銜全球政府舉債新風向：倚重短債融資、壓減長債發行",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"592\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/sPfTbCgJqFt3IUzGdbCYSQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU5MjtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/d93317c05eaadc8c1930e2559dffe31c\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 英國和日本正在響應投資者需求，舉借更多短債。這一策略轉變雖能降低政府當期利息支出，卻使其在債務展期時面臨可能代價不菲的利率波動風險。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">英國將今年長期債券發行量大幅削減至歷史新低，並正在考慮擴大超短期票據市場。長債品種傳統上是政府債務發行的基石。日本在長期債券遭遇拋售後，也在順應市場呼聲，大幅增加短期債務發行。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這些並非孤例。美國正更多地依賴國庫券來彌補聯邦赤字，澳大利亞等國也已提出類似政策。根據彭博綜合指數，全球範圍內政府債券的平均到期年限已跌至2014年以來的最低水平。日本和英國的長期債券認購需求萎縮尤為明顯，促使兩國政府做出最激進的調整。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-7680bbf6-2bf4-357a-b03f-90a2b009e512-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"592\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ZvpwOXK1_ebx8l4GqzenLA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU5MjtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/b450e8dd6cb145170f1f38805f2de70b\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">瑞穗國際駐倫敦策略師Evelyne Gomez-Liechti指出，「風險在於，如果利率上升，利息支出可能會突然大幅增加。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">政府大幅壓縮發債期限，實際上是在押注長期債券殖利率過高且會很快回落。殖利率若是不降反升，當債務需要展期時其成本將會飆升。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「如果年期僅為兩年，那意味著需要非常頻繁地進行再融資，」T&amp;D Asset Management首席策略師Hiroshi Namioka說道，「持續滾動發行短債會引發對財政可持續性的擔憂，而且必須警惕這種操作導致未來財政前景更加難以預測。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管如此，分析人士依然將這些調整視為對投資者需求演變的自然反應。美國財政部長貝森特上個月表示，正在「密切監測特定美國國債品種需求可能出現的潛在長期變化」，並將據此做出調整。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/gB3blc4WrAReP6vqV3KH4g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/ba5b43aa49fb4399c34720125a749b18\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">目前，各國政府可以仰仗一張王牌：主要央行仍維持偏寬鬆貨幣政策。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「英國央行和聯儲會仍有降息空間。日本央行可能被視為風險較高，但我認為其加息周期的步調將有所不同，」瑞穗的Gomez-Liechti說道。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題UK, Japan Lead Global Government Exodus From Long Bond Sales (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Michael MacKenzie、Alex Harris、Takahiko Hyuga、Yuko Takeo.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%92%8C%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E9%A0%98%E9%8A%9C%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E8%88%89%E5%82%B5%E6%96%B0%E9%A2%A8%E5%90%91-%E5%80%9A%E9%87%8D%E7%9F%AD%E5%82%B5%E8%9E%8D%E8%B3%87-%E5%A3%93%E6%B8%9B%E9%95%B7%E5%82%B5%E7%99%BC%E8%A1%8C-090234817.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-03 18:00:59",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "台灣利率市場：公債平靜 央行存單標售利率再跌；提存期底資金寬鬆",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美債10年殖利率持穩在周初彈升後的短線高檔區，台灣公債電子盤周三未成交，在上日標售符合預期後市況回復平靜；央行364天期存單標售利率連八跌，央行官員稱反映銀行有大量配置需求。</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">國票證券債券交易員Sam Chang受訪稱，央行存單標售利率持續走低，意味著資金寬鬆，對公債有支撐作用；但由於附買回利率未跌，各家平均資金成本仍在1.30%上下，公債殖利率的下檔料有限</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">預估10年券在今年年底前於1.32%-1.36%波動</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管聯儲會料再次降息，然而日本央行可能升息，將會牽制台灣央行的降息步調</p></li></ul></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">台灣央行標售364天期存單加權平均得標利率1.228%，較上次下跌3基點，已連續八個月下跌，並進一步朝例行28天期申購利率貼近</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據一位央行官員表示，主要是兩家銀行有大量配置的需求</p></li></ul></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">貨幣市場</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-26aa3b8a-f570-378f-a3c6-ea5a84b35010-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據票券商與銀行人士稱，周三逢提存期底的市況寬鬆，資金需求平淡；銀行對於跨年交易的態度暫時謹慎，目前以月內拆款或月內短票交易為優先。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據一位銀行資金調度人士稱，銀行資金偏鬆但市場上需求不大，藉由申報央行存單來消化餘錢</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">12月資金調度偏謹慎，觀望美、台央行會議與年底季節性因素</p></li></ul></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據三位票券商人士表示，銀行資金寬鬆而積極欲提供拆款，法人亦有資金暫泊，但票券商需求不大；短票交易目前以月內較多，銀行對於跨年交易謹慎</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與銀行承作30天期且跨年的自保短票利率成交在約1.45%-1.47%，成交區間較寬</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">月內短票則視天期在1.43%-1.46%，大致平穩</p></li></ul></li></ul></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">上述交易員不願具名接受採訪，因未被授權公開評論</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">台灣短票市場：30天自保票上交易日平均利率1.449%</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">台灣債券發行預覽：元大金控；興富發建設；匯豐台灣</p></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場動態</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據彭博追蹤櫃買中心數據，10年熱券電子盤無成交</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">5年熱券電子盤無成交</p></li></ul></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">台股加權指數上漲0.8%，報27793.04點</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據彭博數據，5年期利率交換報1.905%，漲1.5基點</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國10年期國債殖利率紐約尾盤報4.0865%，亞洲盤中報4.0749%</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">台北時間下午2:30，據拆款中心數據，隔夜拆款加權平均利率在0.823%，區間在0.805%-0.825%，上日收在0.822%</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">2-7天平均利率在1.423%，區間在1.4%-1.45%</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">上交易日當日超額準備為負722億元台幣；本提存期累計超額準備為1兆4584億元台幣，加計前期1%超額準備為1兆6471億元台幣</p></li></ul></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至上交易日，央行定存單未到期餘額為7兆3881.3億元台幣，上日增發133億元</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">參看台灣央行各天期存單到期落點一覽，點選WSL TWNCD</p></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">重點關注</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普要將鮑威爾接班人懸念留到年後 又稱讚聯儲會“潛在”主席哈塞特</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">摩根大通預計美債殖利率明年將上升 降息預期料減弱</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美銀證券預計日本10年期國債殖利率到2026年底將升至2%</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">[深度] 聯儲會對降息終點的分歧空前 如同暗物質的中性利率究竟在哪</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博經濟研究：凱文·哈塞特領導下的聯儲會會是什麼樣子</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐盟最終敲定協議 將在2027年底前逐步停止從俄羅斯進口天然氣</p></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
